{"tid":687382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[矛盾大作戰]被鬧「港獨」「廢物」 蝗嘉爾發律師信要求網民道歉","createTime":"2018-06-02T08:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T08:18:41.000Z","uid":84032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ddc76a74ae5fa2f8c5fbd9e243a01f01468c2b","tid":687382,"uid":84032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"韓國男團GOT7嘅香港成員Jackson（王嘉爾）喺大陸人氣高企，佢亦要中韓兩邊走，近日有網民就喺微博發表大量具有侮辱性嘅言論，指摘Jackson愛講大話，留言包括「港獨」、「廢物」、「死爹」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\nJackson方面因為被網民侮辱，其工作室噚晚就喺官方微博發表律師信，針對部份微博用戶喺網上發佈有關Jackson不當嘅言論，直指網民嚴重侵犯咗Jackson嘅名譽權，同時要求有關網民要刪除相關言論並作出道歉，又呼籲：「網路不是謠言的避風港，願共同維護和諧自由的網路環境。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180602/58268453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58268453&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=303b6949\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58268453&h=dc082032\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180602/58268453</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都清楚平時Jackson 係幾愛國，今次竟然中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/05/164718_20d358c92b4b3a46d22ffa9b9aee29fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F05%2F164718_20d358c92b4b3a46d22ffa9b9aee29fb.jpg&h=342f67c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ibmFKuLrqCmrQKf8wtrOjtBOlTEeZbjqcvGjw21FIgOV2ww9jVb12wJQDrib2dB7IZnrev9QtvibMYQWytYX5LXhA/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2FibmFKuLrqCmrQKf8wtrOjtBOlTEeZbjqcvGjw21FIgOV2ww9jVb12wJQDrib2dB7IZnrev9QtvibMYQWytYX5LXhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng&h=4eb840a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aNDtWquWofozE5eJVmBnI2OAP1ZSNVgLLwr6ZSAsoTaFxSZXtz4QxIicUSpHlD0Ebg3lq6tLibOmljfXibhnHcu5A/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2FaNDtWquWofozE5eJVmBnI2OAP1ZSNVgLLwr6ZSAsoTaFxSZXtz4QxIicUSpHlD0Ebg3lq6tLibOmljfXibhnHcu5A%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif&h=191326aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/102544K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F102544K.jpg&h=a303ded7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}